<span class="postbody">I understand where you guys are coming from, but understand that they did not effect all trade skills the same.  I am a Provisioner, they number one incresed the power cost 10 fold for us.  But, the buffs we recieve dont work, I mean at all, I cant even use mine, they are completely greyed out since the patch.  Next they nerft times, I mean they nerfted them bad.  Now any single combine drink = 30 or so minutes.  So a tier 5 drink starts out as 30 minutes, who is going to pay the cost it takes to gather resources for that for 30 minutes of good non combat regen?  Not much.  I really think the patch was in most parts bad, for many people, check out the artisan boards, you will see this thread with over 20 posts in there.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
